    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example retains the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and the factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from a recent inspection of the rear subframe mounting points and a refresh of the trailing arm bushings. The VANOS system has been professionally serviced, ensuring precise valve timing across the rev range. Finished in Carbon Black over a well-preserved Nappa leather interior, this vehicle balances mechanical purity with daily usability. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump.",
