    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of a well-cared-for daily driver that remains in impressive shape. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface marks consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show light natural creasing but no tears, and all dashboard electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust and dependable. It has undergone regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance, resulting in a smooth-shifting transmission and a quiet, responsive engine. The brakes feel firm, the suspension provides a comfortable ride without any unusual noises, and the tires have significant tread life remaining. It comes complete with its original owner's manuals, a clean title, and a full set of floor mats. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next journey.",
