      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years, making it a perfect, reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road! I\u2019ve enjoyed every mile, but it\u2019s time for someone else to take the wheel for their own adventures. It runs smooth and is ready to go\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
